description:
Everything this White House said about covid turned out to be untrue. Tablet article about the damage the "covid cult" did to children. Caller and son on brink of being thrown out of military for not getting covid shot. Clay and Buck welcome back Pandemia author and investigative journalist Alex Berenson to update us on the latest urgent covid news. When will there be a reckoning and an apology? C&B take covid calls. Clay: Prosecute Fauci.
